    "description": "<p>Hi There!\nAre you a highly innovative and creative software developer? Do you consider yourself flexible and have an interest for both front- and back-end development challenges? Are you ready to enter the rapidly developing industry of 3D printing solutions? If you answered “yes!” to all 3, then we want you on our team!</p>\n<p>3devo B.V. is a innovative high-tech start-up located in Utrecht, NL, that develops material solutions that contribute to the 3D-printing market. Our flat structure creates an innovative and result-oriented work-space where team members are encouraged to further develop themselves. We work hard, but also enjoy our morning cups of coffee, our (slightly-competitive) foosball games, and team-bonding workout sessions at the company gym. With growth ahead and new challenges to face, this is an exciting time to join 3devo!</p>\n<p>We are looking for a:</p>\n<h2>Full Stack Developer (fulltime 32-40 hrs)</h2>\n<h3>What will you be doing?</h3>\n<p>As a Software Developer you will be part of our new software team to develop, deploy &amp; improve our web based software applications, working hand in hand with our material research, embedded &amp; electronics teams, to help in building the 3devo ecosystem of 3D print material development, research and plastic recycling solutions.\nYour daily activities consist of:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Working on our first generation of web-application(s)</li>\n<li>A broad variation of both front- and back-end development challenges</li>\n<li>Finding smart and elegant solutions for complex problems</li>\n<li>Keeping momentum with quick development iteration cycles</li>\n<li>Testing and validating new developments both internally and with clients</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Do you have what it takes?</h3>\n<p>You are able to work in a team dynamic, but you’re also capable of working independently. Multi-tasking is not an issue for you, since you have a solution-oriented attitude.\nYou get fulfillment out of creating meaningful solutions that make a difference.\nYou have a strong drive to learn, grow and a persevering work mentality. Adequate knowledge and experience is required for this position, but you still feel that there is so much to learn.\nIn addition, you have/are:\n-Bachelor’s degree in computing, computer science, engineering, mathematics, or similar educational background but you are also welcome with a comparable working experience</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>A flexible mindset work both front and back-end, and quickly switch context.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Work experience with the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>JS (Angular, React)</li>\n<li>TypeScript</li>\n<li>Development frameworks like Ionic</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Experience with the following as a bonus:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cloud providers like FireBase, AWS or AZURE</li>\n<li>CSS /HTML5</li>\n<li>Gitlab / CiCD\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>What do we offer?</h3>\n<p>Work alongside innovate minds in a high-tech working environment that is innovating at an ever increasing rate.\nPlus:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We strongly support a work-life balance and encourage agile freedom and flexibility</li>\n<li>Flat hierarchy, short decision lines, big impact</li>\n<li>Good salary and working conditions</li>\n<li>After-work drinks with the  teams on Fridays</li>\n<li>Some awesome 3devo merchandize</li>\n<li>A very lively atmosphere in the office with super colleagues 😊</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested? Send your CV and motivational letter to <a href=\"mailto:hr@3devo.com\">hr@3devo.com</a>.</p>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p>Want to get in touch?\nEmail your Application Letter &amp; Resume to:\n<a href=\"mailto:HR@3devo.com\">HR@3devo.com</a></p>\n",
