    "description": "<p>Intersog® is a Chicago-based provider of ROI-driven custom web and mobile development specializing in the delivery of full-service, end-to-end solutions, and project resources to Fortune 500 companies, SMEs and startups. We help our clients attack their ambitious business goals, solve skills shortage issues and become innovative by building Dedicated Software Development Teams in Vancouver, BC, Canada, and/or providing on-demand IT project resources to complete required skills on their in-house teams.</p>\n<p>We’re looking for an experienced Senior Full Stack JS Developer (with Firebase) who would join the existing development team and help build a modern serverless platform for small-business owners mentorship. The development team consists of 3 smaller teams working remotely from different locations. You will be a part of one of the teams. A lot of communication happens remotely and documenting your work plays a key role.</p>\n<p>Most of the developers can take over any tasks and are not separated into frontend, backend roles, or any other narrow categories. Knowledge sharing is very important to us.</p>\n<p>About the project:</p>\n<p>We are looking for a Senior Full Stack JS Developer (with Firebase) with primary emphasis on Back End to join an existing team to build a rapidly growing platform for small-businesses on serverless infrastructure. The team is distributed in Ukraine, Mexico, Canada; with the Product team and CTO in the US.</p>\n<p>Tech Stack:</p>\n<p>Javascript / Typescript, React.js, Material-UI, Google Cloud, Firebase</p>\n<p>We are looking for:</p>\n<pre><code>- 5+ years building web applications at scale with a primary focus on Back End; \n- Solid experience with Google Firebase.\n- Solid experience with backendless services, preferable Google Firebase.\n- Solid understanding and experience of TypeScript;\n- Solid understanding of SDLC, including design, testing, deployment and quality documentation;\n- Strong communication skills;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Will be a big plus:</p>\n<pre><code>- Experience in a technical leadership role;\n- Experience in architecture design patterns;\n- Excellent problem-solving skills\n- React or similar UI frameworks\n</code></pre>\n<p>What you will be doing:</p>\n<pre><code>- Take a lead role in backend development of platform application using Firebase SDK and related frameworks\n- Design new features and architectural approaches\n- Prototype and develop the modules for the platform\n- Create and maintain asynchronous code\n- Optimize platform for maximum speed and scalability\n</code></pre>\n<p>We offer</p>\n<pre><code>- Competitive compensation based on your skills, experience, and customer satisfaction;\n- Opportunity to work on challenging and exciting international projects;\n- Flexible working hours and the possibility to work remotely when needed;\n- Extended medical and life insurance;\n- Casual, friendly and family work environment\n</code></pre>\n",
