    "title": "Tech Lead",
    "description": "<p>Tech Lead</p>\n<p>About the Interledger Foundation\nInterledger is working towards a more equitable and creative global society through the open exchange of currency. To move this vision forward we will:\nConnect a powerful community of web advocates and leaders\nPromote creative and innovative solutions to connecting humanity\nSteward technology and standards work that advances open payment technology</p>\n<p>About the Role\nThe Interledger Foundation seeks an innovative and creative Tech Lead to join our welcoming and inclusive team.  This position will help drive the adoption of the Interledger Protocol position and contribute to the successful growth of the organization.</p>\n<p>Our Ideal Candidate\nIs as excited about open source technology as we are\nThrives in a startup environment and is a self starter\nWants to be a member of a small and dynamic team</p>\n<p>As Tech Lead You Will\nBe an integral member of the Interledger Community of Developers\nCollaborate with the community and partners to determine and lead which technology based projects and standards work the Foundation will focus on\nDesign, implement, and test software across the Interledger Protocol stack, both frontend and backend\nDeliver presentations related to Interledger at meetings and conferences\nHave an opportunity to build the department and IT team from the ground up</p>\n<p>Your Experience\n5+ years of software development experience on large scale distributed systems\nTrack record of building and maintaining performant micro service oriented software products\nKnow the ins and outs of Node.js and are up for working in Java and Typescript\nDemonstrated ability to proactively manage tasks and projects independently</p>\n<p>Nice To Have\nBS in Computer Science or similar\nHands-on experience with the Interledger Protocol stack and/or Rust\nFamiliarity with the Interledger and/or payments ecosystem</p>\n<p>Location: The Interledger Foundation is a fully remote organization, so this position can be based anywhere</p>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p><a href=\"https://breezy.jobs/p/f987e5f2b793-tech-lead\">https://breezy.jobs/p/f987e5f2b793-tech-lead</a></p>\n",
